            <lg xml:id="TK69">
<l>īṉṟa poḻutiṟ perituvakkun taṉmakaṉaic</l>
<l>cāṉṟō ṉeṉakkēṭṭa tāy</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mother rejoices more even than at his birth, when she hears</l>
<l>her son called a learned man.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
